&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline; color: #5f6368; display: block; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 8px; width: 100%;"&gt;Table 9: Common cloud capabilities for infrastructure hardening&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
