&lt;div class="block-paragraph_advanced"&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Restricting Common Lateral Movement Tools and Methods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Table 17 provides a consolidated summary of security configurations that can be leveraged to combat against common remote access tools and methods used for lateral movement within environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
