&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Attempted Logon of a Privileged Account from a Nonprivileged Access Workstation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style="vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #000000; padding: 16px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1078/" rel="noopener" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;T1078 – Valid Accounts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style="vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #000000; padding: 16px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Search for logon attempts correlating to highly privileged accounts authenticating to systems that reside outside of the Tier 0 layer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
