&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="block-paragraph_advanced"&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Detection Opportunities for the Protected Users Security Group&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
