&lt;td style="vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #000000; padding: 16px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Archive downloaded from &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;130.94.6[.]228&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;. Contained GRIDTIDE.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
