&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Additional archive downloaded. Contained &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;vmlog&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;(renamed to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;fire&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;), a SoftEtherVPN Bridge component.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
