&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style="vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #000000; padding: 16px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;mylingocoin.com&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style="vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #000000; padding: 16px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;Hosted the payload that was retrieved and executed to commence the initial infection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
