&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;After a dormant period, the threat actor used this IP address to login back into the Triofox instance and carry out subsequent activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
